config.text: Import color, text styles and components directly from your Figma file to map them into your CX Design System settings effortlessly.
Paste the Figma file link you want to import styles and components from. Make sure it's accessible via your token.
Enter your Figma personal access token. This is required to fetch styles from your file. How to get it?
Youre agreeing to share personal information with this app. View the developers privacy policy before you share anything with this app.
